ed="T" n="0859c13"/><persName key="A013519">釋普靜</persName>，姓<name>茹</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000005796"><placeName>晉州</placeName><placeName>洪洞</placeName></placeName>人也。少出家于<anchor xml:id="beg0859sgsz21"/>本<anchor xml:id="end0859sgsz21"/><lb
ed="T" n="0859c14"/>郡<persName key="A013520">惠澄<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>。暗誦諸經，明持祕呪，思升白<lb
ed="T" n="0859c15"/>品<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1939"/>，願剪青螺<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1940"/>。既下方壇，而循律檢，往<anchor xml:id="beg0859sgsz23"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0859sgsz23"/><lb
ed="T" n="0859c16"/><placeName key="PL000000042886"><placeName>鳳翔</placeName><placeName>法門寺</placeName></placeName>真身<ptr target="#n2943"/>。乃於<placeName key="PL000000025556">睢陽</placeName>聽涉，赴<placeName key="PL000000058822">龍興<lb
ed="T" n="0859c17"/>寺</placeName>講訓<ptr target="#n2944"/>，徒侶若鱣鮪<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1941"/>之宗蛟龍焉。又允<placeName key="PL000000056158">琴<lb
ed="T" n="0859c18"/>臺</placeName>請轉<name>梵</name>輪<ptr target="#n2945"/>，安而能遷。復於<placeName key="PL000000026072">陳</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000026332">蔡</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000022793">曹</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000016493">亳</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000015988">宿</placeName>、<lb
ed="T" n="0859c19"/><placeName key="PL000000010633">泗</placeName>，各隨緣獎導。迴於今<placeName key="PL000000023467">東京</placeName>揚化<ptr target="#n2946"/>，善者從<lb
ed="T" n="0859c20"/>之。<placeName key="PL000000000124">晉</placeName><date key="j20655272065880" notAfter-iso="+0944-02-01" notBefore-iso="+0943-02-13"><name>天福</name>癸卯歲</date>，心之懷土，還復<ref type="place" target="#PL000000005796">故鄉</ref>。遂<lb
ed="T" n="0859c21"/>斷食發願，願捨千身，速登正覺。至<placeName key="PL000000057658">周</placeName><date key="j20698982070281" notAfter-iso="+0956-02-19" notBefore-iso="+0955-02-01"><name>顯<lb
ed="T" n="0859c22"/>德</name>二年</date><ptr target="#n2948"/>，遇請真身入寺，遂陳狀於州牧<persName key="A013522">楊<lb
ed="T" n="0859c23"/><roleName>君</roleName></persName><ptr target="#n2947"/>，願焚軀供養，<persName key="A013522">楊<roleName>君</roleName></persName>允其意。乃往<placeName key="PL000000058308">廣勝寺</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0859c24"/>傾州民人或獻之香果，或引以<anchor xml:id="beg0859sgsz25"/>旛華<anchor xml:id="end0859sgsz25"/>，或泣<lb
ed="T" n="0859c25"/>淚相隨，或唄聲前導。至<date key="j20699932069993" when-iso="+0955-05-07">四月八日</date>，真身塔前<lb
ed="T" n="0859c26"/>廣發大願曰：「願焚千身，今<anchor xml:id="beg0859sgsz27"/>千<anchor xml:id="end0859sgsz27"/>中之一也。<ptr target="#n2949"/>」徐<lb
ed="T" n="0859c27"/>入柴庵，自分火炬。時則煙飛慘色，香靄愁<lb
ed="T" n="0859c28"/>雲，舉眾<anchor xml:id="beg0859sgsz29"/>歎<anchor xml:id="end0859sgsz29"/>嗟，群黎悲泣。享壽六十有九，弟子<lb
ed="T" n="0859c29"/>等收合餘燼供養焉。</p>
